#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.35"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.35:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.35:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga"
msgstr "4. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.35:0.3"
msgid "35. Paṭhamasāmaññasutta"
msgstr "35. The Ascetic Life (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.35:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.2"
msgid "“Sāmaññañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, sāmaññaphalāni ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the ascetic life and the fruits of the ascetic "
"life."

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, sāmaññaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the ascetic life?"

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.5"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sāmaññaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the ascetic life."

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.8"
msgid "Katamāni ca, bhikkhave, sāmaññaphalāni?"
msgstr "And what are the fruits of the ascetic life?"

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.9"
msgid "Sotāpattiphalaṃ, sakadāgāmiphalaṃ, anāgāmiphalaṃ, arahattaphalaṃ—"
msgstr "The fruits of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, and perfection."

msgctxt "sn45.35:1.10"
msgid "imāni vuccanti, bhikkhave, sāmaññaphalānī”ti."
msgstr "These are called the fruits of the ascetic life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.35:1.11"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
